Written by Ruben Mikkonen, 2012
Released under public domain

shmup is music player written in ash

Usage: shmup [-s] [-r] [-d dir]|less
	-s shuffle on, defaults to off
	-r repeat on, defaults to off
	-d directory, defaults to ~/

There are many ways to close the player.
The best one is, however, probably killing
it. That's why it prints its PID.
